  "prompt": "What are some things I should know about Brunei?",
  "response": "Here are some key facts about Brunei:\n\n1. Location and Geography\n- Located on the north coast of Borneo in Southeast Asia\n- Surrounded by the Malaysian state of Sarawak\n- Small country with approximately 460,000 people\n\n2. Government and Politics\n- Absolute monarchy ruled by Sultan Hassanal Bolkiah\n- One of the world's few remaining absolute monarchies\n- Implements strict Islamic Sharia law\n\n3. Economy\n- Wealthy nation due to extensive oil and natural gas resources\n- High standard of living for citizens\n- No personal income tax\n\n4. Culture\n- Predominantly Muslim country (about 67% of population)\n- Official language is Malay, but English is widely spoken\n- Conservative Islamic culture with strict social norms\n\n5. Notable Features\n- Has one of the world's highest per capita GDPs\n- No alcohol is allowed\n- Very low crime rate\n- Rich biodiversity with extensive rainforests\n\n6. International Relations\n- Member of ASEAN (Association of Southeast Asian Nations)\n- Close ties with Malaysia and Singapore\n- Generally peaceful and diplomatically neutral country\n\nThese points provide a basic overview of Brunei's key characteristics and features.",
